    <abstract audience="internal" id="aspace_a3a9c271d5559e77e885ff0da425f804">The John I. Shafer Jr. papers include correspondence, drafts and reprints of publications and lab notebooks relating to the work of John I. Shafer relating to corn, arginine desimidase in chlorella, and other plant genetics and botany related topics.</abstract>
    <unitid type="bibid">11902542</unitid>
